snippet.title: PROOF Johnny Depp Abused Amber Heard / The Evidence
snippet.description:
Hi there! This video displays the text messages used as evidence in the Johnny Depp v The Sun UK libel case. Depp decided to sue The Sun for publishing an article where they brand him a ‘wife-beater’ for abusing his then wife, Amber Heard. 

The evidence displayed is part of The Sun’s closing argument. Available to read here : https://www.nickwallis.com/closing-submissions

There are a lot of people involved in these texts so here is a rundown on who everyone is:

Johnny Depp                         Claimant
Amber Heard                         Defendant/Witness
Jerry Judge                            Depp’s Bodyguard
Malcolm Connelly                 Depp’s Bodyguard
Kevin Murphy                         Depp’s Bodyguard
Sean Bett                                Depp’s Bodyguard
Stephen Deuters                    Depp’s Assistant
Nathan Holmes                      Depp’s Assistant 
Dr Kipper                                 Depp’s Doctor
Erin Boerum                            Depp’s Nurse 
Debbie Lloyd                           Depp’s Nurse
Bruce Witkin                            Depp’s Friend
Paul Bettany                            Depp’s Friend  
Patti Smith                               Depp’s Friend
Lily-Rose Depp                        Depp’s Daughter
Christi Dembrowski                Depp’s Sister
Christian Carino                      Mutual Friend
Kate James                              Heard’s ex-assistant 
Paige Heard                             Amber’s Mother
David Heard                             Amber’s Father
Whitney Henriquez                 Amber’s Sister
Raquel (Rocky) Pennington  Amber’s Friend
Josh Drew                               Amber’s Friend / Raquel’s Partner
iO Tillet Wright                        Amber’s Friend
Savannah McMillan               Amber’s Friend
Elon Musk “Rocketman”       Amber’s Friend
Amanda de Cadenet             Amber’s Friend
Dr Connell Cowan                 Amber’s Therapist
Jodi Gottlieb                          Amber’s Publicist 
Melanie Inglessis                  Amber’s MUA
Tasya Van Ree                       Amber’s Ex-wife

Comments are disabled to combat abuse.
